Source.Value: Amazon Rekognition is a powerful image and video analysis service provided by AWS that offers machine learning capabilities for identifying objects, people, text, scenes, and activities in images and videos. It enables developers to easily integrate advanced image and video recognition features into their applications without requiring deep expertise in machine learning. Key features of AWS Rekognition include Facial Analysis, Face Recognition, Object and Scene Detection, Text Detection, Celebrity Recognition, Activity Detection. Amazon Rekognition is an excellent choice for developers looking to add advanced vision capabilities to their applications with minimal effort and high reliability. This case type demonstrates Facial analysis capability of Amazon Rekognition.  Add the image link and submit to get the Facial Analysis from Amazon Rekognition.
